

**Matsh ab uhpam i wuhsh g Jesus muhkig t amjed **

*An g neid g Mark 16:1-10; Luke 24:1-12; John 20:1-10 *

1 Sh am e aihim g domig tash. Tsh am hihaꞌini wui hihi g Mary Magdalene heg wehm hema Mary. 

2 D am hahawa si uꞌugij g jewed. Tsh g anghil ab i hud dahm kahchim t amjed k im hu hab i melch g hodai k an dahm dahiwua. 3 Sh g wuhioshaj si s‑masma tonod hab masma mo g wepgi. Sh g wehschugaj hab masma s‑toha mo g s‑mohoni gew. 4 Kutsh wabsh wohoꞌi totods hegam shondal mo ab nuhkud k si gigiwek ch amjed hab sha e juh mo d wabsh koꞌi. 

5 Kush ab neok hegai anghil ch hab kaij ab ha wui hegam uꞌuwi, “Pi g am wo shaꞌi e totodsid. M ani wa s‑mahch mam g Jesus chuhkug an chum gahghim. 6 Ab g wo i hihim k wo nei mo pi ia hu haꞌichug iia mat ia e cheh. Uhpam at ep i wuhsh muhkig amjed mo wa hab wa kaij. 7 Kumt am s‑hohtam wo hihim k wo ha ahgi hegam mo am wehmajkahim mat uhpam e chegito k gam hu wo hih Galilee wui. Mt gam hu wo hihim k am haꞌab wo nei. Neh, am ani em‑ahgid mo has i kaij.” Bash kaij g anghil. 

8 Kutsh si e totodsid k si s‑hohtam ga hu hihi ab amjed g hihaꞌini k eda si s‑hehgig ch ia hu chum wohp matsh wo t‑ahgi. 

9 Tsh wabshaba haha wabsh ha nam g Jesus k hab kaij, “T wo s‑em hoꞌigeꞌel g Jiosh.” Tsh ab si i shul wui k an ui tahtdaj an k ab si ihm. 

10 Sh hab kaij ab ha wui, “Pi g am wo ni‑ehbenid. Am g wo hihim k wo ha ahgi g ni‑wepnag mat am wo hihi Galilee wui k am haꞌab wo ni‑nei.” 

**Matsh haschu ged hu ha ahgi g shondal **

11 Kutsh gam hu hihi hegam uꞌuwi. Tsh hegam shondal mash am nuhkud g hihaꞌini am haꞌi hihim k ged hu dada kihhim t am k am ha ahgi g uꞌugchu papal wehs haꞌichu matsh haschu has i e juh. 

12 Tsh g uꞌugchu papal am ha wehm e nam g geꞌeged k am e aꞌaga k am hahawa muꞌi ha mah g lial idam shondal 13 k hab ha ahg, “Bamt wo chei matki am dada g piongaj chuhug ch ed k am em‑ehs g honshpadag mam kohksh. 14 Kutp wo sha kah g kownal mam has i kaij, tt wo wa em‑doꞌibia.” 

15 Kutsh am ui g lial hegam shondal k am hab e juh mam has i ha ahg. Ia o i idani hab masma am e aꞌaga am ha shahgid g Tutuligo. 

**Matsh g Jesus am i e chehgi ha wui **

*An g neid g Mark 16:14-18; Luke 24:36-49; John 20:19-23; Acts 1:6-8 *

16 Kuchd ahchim gamai hemako am hihi heg wui doꞌag am Galilee ch ed mo wa hab kaij g Jesus matt am wo hihi. 17 D g Jesus am haꞌichug. Kuchd ab si ihm. D eda hi wa haꞌi sha pi wohoch. 

18 D ab si i t‑miabi g Jesus k hab kaij ab t‑wui, “Jiosh at ab ni‑mah g gewkdag wehs haꞌichu dahm an dahm kahchim ch ed ch id dahm jewed. 19 Gamai g wo hihim wehsko hemajkam ha wui k wo i ha mashcha g haꞌichu ni‑ahga k ab wo i ha pahl wapko am chehchegch g ni‑ohg Jiosh ch ahni ep ni‑chehcheg mani d alidaj ch heg ehp Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag. 20 Ab ani em‑chehani mamt has wo masmak. Kumt ab wo i ha mashcha g hemajkam mat ab wo s‑wohog elidad wehs haꞌichu mani haschu ab em‑chehani. Kunt chum hekid wo em‑wehmajk, chum as wo huhug g jewed.”


